## PROJECT IDENTITY

This workspace contains the fractal-enhanced topological quantum
computing research publication suite: three LaTeX manuscripts
targeting arXiv (quant-ph), Physical Review X, and Optica, plus
supporting figures, Python simulation scripts, bibliography files,
and cover letters.

The primary goal is **clean LaTeX compilation** to produce
submission-ready PDFs with proper citation resolution and figure
rendering. No content rewriting. No refactoring. Compilation and
error-fixing only.

